creator: DuPont Sustainable Solutions
descriptionHtml:
Enable the future of operational risk and safety management with DSS Transform by DuPont Sustainable Solutions.

This highly adaptable, cloud-based EHS digital platform enables organisations to digitise their operational and risk management processes. Based on decades of proven best practices and methodologies in workplace safety, change management & culture transformation, DSS Transform helps organisations save time, improve data accuracy, and extract relevant insights for real-time decision making.

From safety management system improvements, to business continuity management, and crisis response, DSS Transform can help.

Modules include:
- Incident management
- Managing workplace & process risks
- Managing contractors
- Managing change
- Employee engagement
- Business continuity management
- Leadership suite
descriptionShort: DSS Transform provides functionality for digitising safety management processes.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Added Portuguese language support for Brazil.
